          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-400-0202-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-400-0202-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-400-0202-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE Sage, who said he should be proud</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-2" n="2">Of Windows in his Breast;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-3" n="3">Because he ne'er one Thought allow'd</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-4" n="4">That might not be confess't:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-5" n="5">His Window scrawl'd by ev'ry Rake,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-6" n="6">His Breast again would cover,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-7" n="7">And fairly bid the D────l take</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-0202-line-8" n="8">The Di'mond and the Lover.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
